<pre>
; This G-code probes the X0 position from the left.

o103 sub

M101 ; Ask user about the probe diameter

M70 ; Save modal state
G91 ; Relative/incremental movements
G20 ; Inches

M100 P1; Enable probe input mask
G38.2 X1.0 F10.0 ; Probe right at fast speed to get close
M100 P0; Disable probe input mask
F20 G01 X-0.1 ; Left 0.1

M100 P1; Enable probe input mask
G38.2 X1.0 F2.5 ; Probe right at medium speed; more precise
M100 P0; Disable probe input mask
F20 G01 X-0.05 ; Left 0.05

M100 P1; Enable probe input mask
G38.2 X1.0 F0.5 ; Probe right at slowest speed; most precise
M100 P0; Disable probe input mask
; Set G54 instead of G92 since that is consistent
; with what AXIS "Touch Off" buttons do
G10 L20 P1 X[-0.125 - #<_hal[probe-radius]> ] ; Set G54 X offset so current X is -0.125

G90 ; Absolute movements
G54 ; Select the co-ordinate system just zero'd
G0 X-0.5 ; Move clear of zero

M72 ; Restore modal state

o103 endsub
</pre>
